      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 10:24",
      "text": "ܠܐ ܐܢܫ ܕܢܦܫܗ ܢܗܘܐ ܒܥܐ ܐܠܐ ܟܠܢܫ ܐܦ ܕܚܒܪܗ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "peshitta:first-corinthians.10.25",
      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 10:25",
      "text": "ܟܠܡܕܡ ܕܡܙܕܒܢ ܒܡܩܠܘܢ ܗܘܝܬܘܢ ܐܟܠܝܢ ܕܠܐ ܥܘܩܒܐ ܡܛܠ ܬܐܪܬܐ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
