      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 10:26",
      "text": "ܕܡܪܝܐ ܗܝ ܓܝܪ ܐܪܥܐ ܒܡܠܐܗ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "peshitta:first-corinthians.10.27",
      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 10:27",
      "text": "ܐܢ ܐܢܫ ܕܝܢ ܡܢ ܚܢܦܐ ܩܪܐ ܠܟܘܢ ܘܨܒܝܢ ܐܢܬܘܢ ܠܡܐܙܠ ܟܠܡܕܡ ܕܡܬܤܝܡ ܩܕܡܝܟܘܢ ܐܟܘܠܘ ܕܠܐ ܥܘܩܒܐ ܡܛܠ ܬܐܪܬܐ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
