      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 10,
      "verseNumber": 32,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 10:32",
      "text": "ܕܠܐ ܬܘܩܠܐ ܗܘܘ ܠܝܗܘܕܝܐ ܘܠܐܪܡܝܐ ܘܠܥܕܬܗ ܕܐܠܗܐ ܀",
